%package devel
Summary:	Headers for OpenAL
Summary(pl):	Pliki nag³ówkowe do OpenAL
Group:		Development/Libraries
Requires:	%{name} = %{version}

%description devel
Header files for OpenAL-based programs.

%description devel -l pl
